    <item>
      <title>Minted Component Library</title>
      <link>http://travisbeckham.com/projects/minted-component-library/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Jan 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://travisbeckham.com/projects/minted-component-library/</guid>
      <description>As Minted Wedding Websites moved from the legacy Hitched Up app to React, it gave me to opportunity to create a responsive component library from the ground up. This library has allowed our team build consistently, launch new features at a faster pace, and reduce internal miscommunication.  The building blocks are broken down into four categories:   Foundation contains the abstract properties such as font definitions, colors, grid structure, and spacing.</description>
